data.description: BACK ON MARKET!! BRING YOUR BUYERS! Well maintained 3/2 Ranch Cul-de-sac lot in the heart of coveted Dacula school district, with schools all under 2 miles away! Property boasts NEW CARPET throughout, a private backyard and large patio great for entertaining, while larger front yard is complete with sprinkler system for easy maintenance. Minutes away from SEVERAL of the BEAUTIFUL PARKS that Dacula has to offer (1.5 Miles to Dacula Park; 1.2 Miles to Rabbit Hill Park), as well as shopping, groceries, post office, and more all within reach! Carlton Chase offers a quite and peaceful setting in a well kept neighborhood, perfect for a family! SUPER EASY ACCESS to 316 (University Pkwy)- Just take a right out of the neighborhood! - only 1.2 miles; 1.6 Miles to Dacula HS; 1.7 Miles to Dacula MS; 1.1 Miles to Dacula ES; 1.5 Miles to Dacula Park; 1.2 Miles to Rabbit Hill Park 4.1 Miles to Freemans's Mill Park; 4.4 Miles to Mulberry Park This one will not disappoint!
